title: 2,500 National Grid customers in Amherst hit by outage blamed on winds
text:
Published By: Buffalow News: Northtowns - Today 
Winds gusting up to 31 mph took down one power line in Amherst Saturday night, cutting service to 2,500 customers, a National Grid spokesman...
